@DATABASE "Micronaut One"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - M - Micronaut One"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - M
                   ====================================

                               Micronaut One
                               =============



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Energy  " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(34650,0) ZXAMPoke(34651,195)"}       34650,0:34651,195
@{"Turn at speed    " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(52004,0) ZXAMPoke(52005,0)"}       52004,0:52005,0
@{"Turbo accelerator" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(52150,81)"}       52150,81
@{"Super brakes     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(52163,62)"}       52163,62
@{"Smooth Walls     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(52591,0)"}       52591,0
@{"Clouds = Energy  " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(34768,107)"}       34768,107
@{"Energy = x       " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(33370,255)"}       33370,x (x= 1-255)

                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).

                         All these POKEs work as far as I can tell, but then
                         I can't play this game anyway :)

                         Rastan
@endnode
